{"tid":2190923,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"林一鳴博士正式轉呔，投資物業不是良好選擇，「買樓收租得個兩厘真係好少」","createTime":"2020-09-06T05:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T04:29:04.000Z","uid":187232,"like":14,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca819785717d3a50c1f61aa55e273f1662a3a4d","tid":2190923,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"作為所謂嘅物業投資專家<br />\n永遠只會睇好樓市<br />\n日日喺度鳩噏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但今日他終於清醒了<br />\n<br />\n終於明白了<br />\n<br />\n終於醒覺了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢於今集CC TVb 「樓計專家」<br />\n親口承認投資物業係不值得<br />\n<br />\n佢今日早餐食完豆沙包之後<br />\n正式同傳媒講<br />\n「買樓收租得個兩厘真係好少」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係之前比佢水左d人<br />\n借三十年按揭<br />\n只有聽日早啲起身返工<br />\n繼續做樓奴<br />\n咁就一世搭地鐵<br />\n一生一半人工唔知供咗d乜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住買樓是長遠投資<br />\n<br />\n唔好再聽KOL<br />\n9up<br />\n佢發表言論唔使負責任<br />\n<br />\n但你成副身家擺落去<br />\n要諗吓下一步<br />\n你有冇錢供樓"},{"pid":"22a59097d47f5d6fe3c1f2299ae324811fadb675","tid":2190923,"uid":343754,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"佢轉頭allin落去又會話你知?<br />\n大把人口不對心"},{"pid":"a19e7459510c3c2d30d5b7170f461261886fac2f","tid":2190923,"uid":70977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"專家食屎喇.jpg <br />\n<br />\n要召喚埋唔買樓買5號仔篇潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ddafd2eef2753d49ac02b9682d2a2db766913f","tid":2190923,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"22a59097d47f5d6fe3c1f2299ae324811fadb675","tid":2190923,"uid":343754,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"佢轉頭allin落去又會話你知?<br />\n大把人口不對心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"佢依家叫人買外國樓賺仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0863b7714f5a04063659328c471abf19dd9aa