e daily <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n博士又<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">燈</span></span></span></span>中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a40ff96a8342f991a36b95e38f2a1dadde88114","tid":2190923,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ab09afbf9ab1b052e92209798dc2a597429f6aa","tid":2190923,"uid":187232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f49344f439cc3aa42bee0eea61933efc78672f5e","tid":2190923,"uid":187232,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a19e7459510c3c2d30d5b7170f461261886fac2f","tid":2190923,"uid":70977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"專家食屎喇.jpg <br />\n<br />\n要召喚埋唔買樓買5號仔篇潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0CEx0BY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0CEx0BY.png&h=bd6d3715&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:46:01.000Z","msg":"紀惠集團行政總裁湯文亮早前售出觀塘工廈套現約8,500萬元，並於滙豐（005）跌穿40元時購入216.5萬股。他向本報書面解釋：「買入滙豐貪其大手買賣容易，易於套現，暫無打算買其他銀行股。」至於股價走勢，他指要賣的人已經沽貨，短期股價應該企穩；中期方面，當香港解封，國內人會到香港買股票，估計屆時有不俗升幅。<br />\n<br />\n他指取消派息不是由滙豐做主動，「估計有英國銀行不能派息，所以英國監管機構才要求全部英倫銀行不派息。」他又認為疫情環球大爆發，這兩、三年不能符合《巴三》（資本比率）情有可原，「監管機構可能太過嚴謹。」<br />\n<br />\n就住淨息差收窄壓力以及壞賬的影響，湯文亮指「不單止滙豐要面對，所有銀行都要面對，淨息差收窄已經很多年，點解今年才要面對？」至於壞賬，他認為在全球量化寬鬆下，壞賬亦不算問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020-4-20apple daily <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n博士又<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">燈</span></span></span></span>中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"剩係匯豐都輸緊20%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal